. di " "
 

. di "When mad>0, fraction of category-years where log(3) cap is the binding co
> nstraint"
When mad>0, fraction of category-years where log(3) cap is the binding constrai
> nt

. qui count if mad > 0

. local denom = r(N)

. qui count if mad > 0 & 3*mad > log(3)

. di "  3*MAD > log(3) (cap binds): " r(N)/`denom'*100 "%"
  3*MAD > log(3) (cap binds): 41.504357%

. qui count if mad > 0 & 3*mad > log(5)

. di "  3*MAD > log(5)            : " r(N)/`denom'*100 "%"
  3*MAD > log(5)            : 4.1863613%

. qui count if mad > 0 & 3*mad > log(10)

. di "  3*MAD > log(10)           : " r(N)/`denom'*100 "%"
  3*MAD > log(10)           : .7476266%

. di " "
 

. di "Drop rate at different caps (cumulative; current = cap3)"
Drop rate at different caps (cumulative; current = cap3)

. qui count

. local n = r(N)

. qui count if would_drop_cap3

. di "  cap = log(3)  drops " r(N)/`n'*100 "%"
  cap = log(3)  drops 5.9246746%

. qui count if would_drop_cap5

. di "  cap = log(5)  drops " r(N)/`n'*100 "%"
  cap = log(5)  drops 5.0177851%

. qui count if would_drop_cap10

. di "  cap = log(10) drops " r(N)/`n'*100 "%"
  cap = log(10) drops 4.808751%

. qui count if would_drop_no_cap

. di "  no cap (3*MAD only) drops " r(N)/`n'*100 "%"
  no cap (3*MAD only) drops 4.808751%

. 
